      Build with Nodewood
    </a> <div class="search-box"><input aria-label="Search" autocomplete="off" spellcheck="false" value=""> <!----></div></div> <div class="bg-red-700 text-white fixed transform rotate-45 px-16" style="top: 20px; right: -40px">
    BETA
